* Database will be in a new folder inside the data folder.
* Each table will be a new file in the folder of database.

-> (To decide about csv or xml or some other format)

* Users and their permissions will be stored in data/users file
* All these library files will be stored in data/lib folder
* There will be a config.php script which includes all these lib files and starts the db

=> Useful functions
* eval(), shell_exec(), unlink(), mkdir(), rmdir(), scandir(), chdir(), getcwd()

=> Useful Techniques
* Variable Variables
* Type casting

=> If using csv
* fgetcsv() and fputcsv()
* A seperate file in the database folder to store that data structure of tables.
